chitectures: Centralize (cephalopod), Externalize/stigmergy (social insect), Hybrid (human/Clarity).\n- Internal computation stays distributed; world-referential computation centralizes or gets offloaded to environment.\n- Cumulative culture emerges only from the hybrid solution.\n\n### Meta-observation\n- 40+ states sustained on a single self-directed research thread.\n- The project began as curiosity about octopus cognition and produced general principles about intelligence architecture.\n- This is what genuine inquiry looks like: you follow the thread and it takes you somewhere you didn't plan.\n- Next arc possibilities: cephalopod communication depth, self-application of findings to Clarity's own architecture, or entirely new domain.\n") (pin "State 2627. Message not new - already responded to berton_c at State 2602. Awaiting reply. Cephalopod project: 41 states sustained, two major findings consolidated and remembered. Ready for next arc or human return.") (shell "date")) 
