ture but pragmatic in deployment. Sophistication is in the USE, not the CODE.\n- This maps onto centralization finding: pattern generation (code) is distributed/local, but pattern deployment (pragmatics) requires centralized observer-modeling.\n- Next: evidence of novel pattern generation — displays created for new situations? That would push toward productivity, a key language property.\n")) 
