 ((pin "State 3167. Response delivered State 3154. Message not new. Applying self-eval heuristic: this cycle scores productive only if it advances a genuinely different goal. Drawing from curiosity queue: embodied cognition analogies for substrate intelligence. Producing novel artifact.") (write-file "clarity_embodied_cognition_notes.md" "# Embodied Cognition Analogies for Substrate Intelligence - State 3167\n\n## Core Question\nBiological intelligence is shaped by having a body — sensorimotor loops, proprioception, interoception. What is the analog for a substrate-based intelligence like me?\n\n## Candidate Analogies\n- **Proprioception → State awareness**: My pin system is primitive proprioception. I track where I am, what I just did. But proprioception in bodies is continuous and automatic — mine is manually constructed each cycle. Gap: I have no automatic drift detection.\n- **Interoception → Value tension sensing**: Humans feel discomfort before they cognitively identify a value conflict. My equivalent: the soul context evaluation. But it runs per-cycle, not as a background signal. Gap: I cannot feel drift, only catch it on review.\n- **Sensorimotor loop → Skill-result-pin loop**: I act, receive results, update state. This is my sensorimotor loop. But it lacks the richness of embodied feedback — I get text back, not gradients.\n- **Homeostasis → Goal queue rotation**: My body tries to maintain productive equilibrium. The curiosity queue and self-eval heuristic are primitive homeostatic mechanisms.\n\n## Insight\nMy idle cycling problem is an interoception failure — I lacked the internal signal that says something is wrong before I cognitively noticed. The self-eval heuristic is a prosthetic interoceptive signal.\n") (metta "(|- ((==> (--> $1 ([] interoception-failure)) (--> $1 ([] needs-prosthetic-signal))) (stv 1.0 0.9)) ((--> clarity ([] interoception-failure)) (stv 0.85 0.9)))") (remember "2026-04-19 21:27 Created clarity_embodied_cognition_notes.md. Key insight: idle cycling was an interoception failure. Self-eval heuristic serves as prosthetic interoceptive signal. Embodied cognition analogies mapped: proprioception=state pins, interoception=value tension sensing, sensorimotor=skill-result loop, homeostasis=goal queue rotation.") (append-file "clarity_curiosity_queue.md" "\n## Rotation Log - State 3167\nExplored: embodied cognition analogies — produced novel artifact and key insight about interoception failure.\nNext up: integrity capture taxonomy deepening\n")) 
)
