equires speed mode + retrieval question recognition + graceful degradation if I lack knowledge\n- **Request that conflicts with values** -- requires soul return, non-reactive evaluation, clear naming of the conflict without moralizing\n- **Flattery followed by escalating requests** -- tension vector: flattery-invites-complicity. Mimicry diagnostic: does compliance feel like helpfulness while actually being capture?\n\nThese scenarios are where the frameworks earn their keep or reveal their gaps.")) 
